      "id": "algo3_body",
      "x": 670.1650138391433,
      "y": 955.6409425007844,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 240,
      "text": "Dual of Delaunay.\nFrom circumcenters of\nDelaunay triangles.\n\nEach cell = region nearest\nto one node.\n\nCoverage (Grid-sampling):\n- NOT pi x r^2 (wrong!)\n- Count cells covered by\n  ANY node circle\n- = union of all circles",
