      "width": 232,
      "height": 240,
      "text": "BFS Connectivity:\n- In-range edges only\n- All reachable = Connected\n\nHealth Score (0-100):\nCoverage:  covPct/100 x 40\nConnected: yes=30 no=0\nBattery:   /400 x 20\nSpacing:   10 / 5 / 0\n\nRecs: Coverage/Connectivity\nBattery/Placement/RF/Nodes",
